# Test Appointment Management Endpoints

## 1. Create Appointment (Admin/Reception/Patient)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/appointments
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": "PATIENT_ID_HERE",
  "doctorId": "DOCTOR_ID_HERE",
  "date": "2026-02-10",
  "time": "10:00",
  "reason": "Regular checkup",
  "notes": "Patient has mild fever"
}

###

## 2. Get All Appointments (with pagination)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/appointments?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

## 3. Get All Appointments (filter by status)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/appointments?status=pending
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

## 4. Get All Appointments (filter by date)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/appointments?date=2026-02-10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

## 5. Get All Appointments (combined filters)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/appointments?status=approved&date=2026-02-10&sort=time&order=asc
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

## 6. Get Appointments by Doctor
GET http://localhost:5000/api/appointments/doctor/DOCTOR_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

## 7. Get Appointments by Doctor (with status filter)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/appointments/doctor/DOCTOR_ID_HERE?status=approved
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

## 8. Get Appointments by Patient
GET http://localhost:5000/api/appointments/patient/PATIENT_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

## 9. Get Single Appointment
GET http://localhost:5000/api/appointments/APPOINTMENT_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

## 10. Update Appointment (Admin/Reception/Doctor)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/appointments/APPOINTMENT_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "approved",
  "date": "2026-02-10",
  "time": "11:00",
  "notes": "Appointment confirmed"
}

###

## 11. Send Email Notification (Admin/Reception)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/appointments/APPOINTMENT_ID_HERE/notify
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

## 12. Delete Appointment (Admin Only)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/appointments/APPOINTMENT_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###
